Kidnappers on Wednesday night abducted the Magajin Garin Daura, Musa Umar, in his Daura residence.

According to report the attackers shot sporadically to disperse the crowd before abducting Umar, a retired customs comptroller after observing the Magrib prayer.

The traditional ruler is the father of Fatima Musa, wife of Colonel Mohammed Abubakar, the Aide de Camp, ADC, to President Muhammadu Buhari.
